    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Candles used during the Christian sacrament of baptism; in many customs, the candle is kept by the baptized person as a symbolic momento.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
